&lt;p&gt;&#8226; UDF Guide  - updated &quot;Accumulator Interface&quot; section (minor edits)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(2) &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1123&quot; title=&quot;Popularize usage of default_parallel keyword in Cookook and Latin Manual&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-1123&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-1123&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

